OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy day,
OL,6,Fespecially across western hills where
OL,7,Fit will be quite misty. A chance of
OL,8,Fsome light rain during the morning.
OL,9,FSunny intervals developing in the east
OL,10,Flater in the day. Winds easing. Warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy over western hills
OL,13,Fwith light drizzle and fog patches.
OL,14,FClear spells further east allowing
OL,15,Fsome mist patches to form. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
