OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA largely cloudy day with
OL,6,Fsome mist and light rain over hills.
OL,7,FTurning brighter through the
OL,8,Fafternoon, especially further east
OL,9,Fwhere it will be quite warm. Light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,13,Fand sunny to end the week. Light
OL,14,Fwinds, though breezier across hills
OL,15,Fand on Friday. Temperatures
OL,16,Fincreasing, becoming very warm or hot.
OL,17,FPerhaps an isolated heavy shower on
OL,18,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
